{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"97f9a1eade","title":"井冈山红卫兵第三号决议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3aad1f3d18","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"97f9a1eade","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"550a5d8a4b","name":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c4d708a2e9","type":"title","text":"井冈山红卫兵第三号决议","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43b0a93388","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山红卫兵第三号决议","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8e20b3366","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc7d585276","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.09.28","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ab63bf99d","type":"paragraph","text":"成立原因","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1b3da585d","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么要成立井冈山红卫兵？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"683f4fd7ea","type":"paragraph","text":"在全国内，十六条的贯彻，遭到极大的阻力，革命造反精神没有得到充分发扬。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a12fb1ab04","type":"paragraph","text":"北京是如此，清华园内更是如此。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b86a166a7c","type":"paragraph","text":"清华园内，清华大学红卫兵忠实地执行工作组的形“左”而实右的路线。毛泽东思想红卫兵则不敢抵制这条错误路线，使得这样一条错误路线畅通无阻。在八·二四以后充分暴露了他先天不足的软弱性。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ae7e342e4","type":"paragraph","text":"为了坚决地抵制，反对这条形“左”实右的路线，坚决把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底，彻底完成毛主席交给我们的一斗二批三改的伟大任务。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a658613085","type":"paragraph","text":"我们向清华大学全体革命师生员工郑重宣告：","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8f81ae5e6","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵诞生了！他在无产阶级文化大革命的洪流中开航了。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d51bef5119","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们高声欢呼，举起你的双手欢迎它吧！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17303d0ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"最后的胜利属于我们，未来的世界是属于我们的！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da06cfc59e","type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"97f9a1eade","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}